  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个用户旅程图，记录我典型工作日的一天。整体分为两大块：去上班和下班回家。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "journey",
        "section Go to work",
        "section Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两段式结构。那标题就叫\"My working day\"可以吗？还有，每个步骤需要标注满意度评分和参与角色吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title My working day",
        "levels",
        "Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标题就用这个。去上班那段，我早上会先泡茶，这个体验很好，给5分；然后上楼去书房，一般般，3分；实际干活的时候最痛苦，只有1分，而且我家猫会来捣乱，所以参与角色要加上Cat。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea: 5: Me",
        "Go upstairs: 3: Me",
        "Do work: 1: Me, Cat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，去上班那段已经画好了。那下班回家那段呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Go to work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "下班回家就轻松多了。下楼是5分，然后坐下来休息也是5分，都是我一个人。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go downstairs: 5: Me",
        "Sit down: 5: Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，下班回家这段只有两个步骤：下楼和坐下，满意度都是满分，只有你自己参与。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Go home",
        "Go downstairs",
        "Sit down"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这样。对了，这个图最好加上无障碍描述，方便屏幕阅读器使用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "accTitle",
        "accDescr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
